Detailed Description

cvmx_ocx_win_cmd

For diagnostic use only. This register is typically written by hardware after accesses to the SLI_WIN_* registers. Contains the address, read size and write mask to used for the window operation. Write data should be written first and placed in the OCX_WIN_WR_DATA register. Writing this register starts the operation. A second write to this register while an operation is in progress will stall.
